commit.message:

	* config/abi/post/solaris2.10/baseline_symbols.txt: Likewise.
	* config/abi/post/solaris2.10/amd64/baseline_symbols.txt: Likewise.
	* config/abi/post/solaris2.10/sparcv9/baseline_symbols.txt: Likewise.

From-SVN: r184776
